# Bowlvana - Açaí Bowl E-commerce Website

## Project Overview
Bowlvana is an e-commerce website specializing in açaí bowls, offering a seamless shopping experience with user authentication, product browsing, cart management, and order processing.

# Bowlvana E-commerce Website
