## Tools & Frameworks Used

### Frontend
- HTML5 & CSS3 (60% custom CSS, 40% framework)
- Vanilla JavaScript
- Google Fonts
- Font Awesome Icons

### External Libraries & Resources
  - Font Awesome 6.0.0 (Icons)
  - Google Fonts
  - Bodoni Moda
  - Playfair Display
  - Montserrat
  - Ramaraja
  - Garamond

### Data Storage
- LocalStorage for persistent data
- JSON for data structure

## File Structure & Purpose

### HTML Files
bowlvana/
├── HTML Files
│   ├── index.html          # Landing page 
│   ├── menu.html           # Product catalog
│   ├── cart.html           # Shopping cart
│   ├── login.html          # Authentication
│   ├── registration.html   # User signup
│   ├── account.html        # User dashboard
│   ├── aboutus.html        # Company info
│   └── order_history.html  # Order tracking
│
├── CSS Files
│   ├── styles.css          # Global styles
│   ├── menu.css           # Menu-specific styles
│   ├── cart.css           # Cart page styles
│   ├── login.css          # Authentication styles
│   └── registration.css    # Registration form styles
│
├── JavaScript Files
│   ├── cart.js            # Cart functionality
│   ├── analytics.js       # User analytics
│   └── main.js            # Core functionality
│
└── assets/
    └── images/            # Product & UI images

### JavaScript Features
- User authentication (registration/login)
- Shopping cart with localStorage
- Invoice generation
- User analytics

### LocalStorage Implementation
- User data storage
- Cart management
- Order history
- Session handling

## Testing the Features
1. **Registration & Login**
   - Use registration form to create account
   - Login with provided test account

2. **Shopping**
   - Browse products in menu
   - Add items to cart
   - Proceed to checkout

3. **Account Features**
   - View order history
   - Check analytics
   - Generate invoices

### Analytics
Access user demographics and invoice data through:
- ShowUserFrequency() - Demographics dashboard
- ShowInvoices() - Full invoice search
- GetUserInvoices() - User-specific invoices

## Registration & Login
- Navigate to 'Registration' in top menu
- Enter required details including TRN
- Use login page for returning users

## Shopping Cart
- Add items using 'Add to Cart' button
- View cart by clicking cart icon
- Adjust quantities or remove items
- Enter Shipping Information and payment type
- Proceed to checkout

## Order Management
- Track orders in 'Order History'
- View invoices
- Download or print invoices

## User Dashboard
- Access profile settings